    	GROUP BY b.codmedico ),0)  ) ) total_ventas 
		From VIEW_Ventas_Medicos c 
    	WHERE  (fechafac BETWEEN '05-01-2019' and '05-20-2019') AND (c.statfact <> '2') AND (c.Prod_serv = 'P') and c.codmedico in(  select Codmedico from Mmedicos where activo=1  and Codmedico<>'000' ) 
    	GROUP BY c.codmedico
